<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6899] [Coprocessors] Add system coprocessor configuration directives</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6899</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Users can supply per-CP configuration for table coprocessors by way of the table CP spec in HTableDescriptor. We have no similar facility for system coprocessors (those installed on all regions via Configuration). We should add support to set per-CP configuration for system CPs also via Configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
